# Atlas CODEOWNERS
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Code owners listed here are automatically requested for review on PRs
# touching the matched paths. Combined with branch protection requiring
# CODEOWNERS review, this ensures the right person is consulted on
# security-sensitive areas (auth, CRF/REDCap client, CI/CD, etc.).
#
# Note: bus-factor is currently 1. To strengthen review coverage, add
# secondary maintainers to the high-risk paths below.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Default owner (catch-all)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*                                       @chasset

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Security-sensitive areas — require explicit review
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Authentication & session handling
/packages/auth/                         @chasset
/packages/baas/                         @chasset

# REDCap API client (handles tokens, data export/import)
/packages/crf-client/                   @chasset
/packages/crf-core/                     @chasset
/services/crf/                          @chasset

# CI/CD workflows
/.github/workflows/                     @chasset
/.github/dependabot.yml                 @chasset
/.github/CODEOWNERS                     @chasset
/scripts/release/                       @chasset

# Security & policy documents
/SECURITY.md                            @chasset
/.gitleaks.toml                         @chasset
/lefthook.yml                           @chasset

# Workspace root (publish config, overrides, scripts)
/package.json                           @chasset
/pnpm-workspace.yaml                    @chasset
/pnpm-lock.yaml                         @chasset
/.npmrc                                 @chasset

# Test fixtures with potentially sensitive REDCap schema
/fixtures/crf-projects/                 @chasset
/scripts/crf-trame/                     @chasset
